id: pm-28cf
title: "Search config normalization (GH-244 follow-up): empty provider adapter strings should auto-normalize"
description: "Tracks GitHub issue #244: empty search.provider/vector_store.adapter strings should not persist as misleading not-configured values after runtime auto-detection."
